headline: Paychex, Inc. Schedules Third Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings Conference Call for March 26, 2025
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., March 12, 2025--Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX) will release financial results for its fiscal 2025 third quarter ended February 28, 2025 via Business Wire before the financial markets open on Wednesday, March 26, 2025.
